OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,F10% of female survey respondents
OL,8,Freported experiencing sexual
OL,9,Fharassment, with the report suggesting
OL,10,Fsexual assault or harassment continues
OL,11,Fto go largely underreported.
OL,13,FMeanwhile, while the report into North
OL,14,FWales Fire Service acknowledged some
OL,15,Fimprovements in culture, bullying and
OL,16,Fharassment continued to be
OL,17,F'widespread' in the service, with over
OL,18,Ftwo-fifths (42%) of survey respondents
OL,19,Freporting personal experiences since
OL,20,FJune 2021, and nearly half (49%) had
OL,21,Fwitnessed such behaviours.
