OL,7,FSurvey respondents described feeling
OL,8,F"unsafe" by "abusive, confrontational"
OL,9,Fsenior leaders.
OL,11,FThe reports were conducted by Crest
OL,12,FAdvisory, a consultancy and research
OL,13,Forganisation based in London that has
OL,14,Falso worked on reviews into culture
OL,15,Fand standards at the Metropolitan
OL,16,FPolice.
OL,18,FWorkplace culture at the Welsh fire
OL,19,Fservices has been under the spotlight
OL,20,Ffor some time.
