OL,7,FITV Wales revealed allegations of a
OL,8,Ftoxic culture at both North Wales Fire
OL,9,Fand Rescue Service and Mid and West
OL,10,FWales Fire and Rescue Service earlier
OL,11,Flast year.
OL,13,FAn investigation saw more than 35
OL,14,Fwhistleblowers raising serious
OL,15,Fconcerns about behaviour in the North
OL,16,FWales service.
