OL,7,FMeanwhile, a damning culture review at
OL,8,FSouth Wales' service was published in
OL,9,FJanuary 2024 and was sparked by an ITV
OL,10,FNews investigation into claims of
OL,11,Fabuse and harassment of female staff
OL,12,Fby male firefighters. It led to the
OL,13,Fthen Fire Chief, Huw Jakeway, stepping
OL,14,Fdown.
